The paper proposes a method for semantic text search that utilizes ontological features of named entities and their latent relationships. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories related to information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computational linguistics (cs.CL), databases (cs.DB), and machine learning (cs.LG). Among these, cs.IR is the most likely category as the paper focuses on improving search quality.
